Contact Us We’d love to hear from you! Whether you have questions about our services, need a quote for your event, or just want to learn more about what we do, feel free to reach out. At Gav’s Kitchen, we’re here to bring exceptional catering to your production, no matter the scale or style. From films and TV dramas to commercials and music videos, our team specialises in delivering delicious meals that keep your cast and crew energised and focused. We pride ourselves on being highly adaptable to budgets while maintaining the quality and service you expect. Get in touch with us today to discuss your needs, and let us help make your production a success with catering tailored to your vision!
